{%- comment -%}
  Ganguram — cart delivery progress + service options panel (Phase 2.11C).

  Read-only markup, rendered at the top of the cart (drawer + page) when the cart
  has items. Populated client-side by assets/ganguram-delivery-progress.js from
  window.GanguramDeliveryRules (getProgressData / getServiceOptions) + the selected
  delivery location. Starts hidden; shows only when admin delivery rules resolve.
  data-gdpr-cart-total carries the live cart total in PAISE (re-rendered on cart
  updates). Display/advisory only — no cart/checkout logic here.
{%- endcomment -%}
<div class="ganguram-delivery-progress" data-ganguram-delivery-progress data-gdpr-cart-total="{{ cart.total_price }}" hidden>
  <div class="ganguram-delivery-progress__bar" role="progressbar" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" data-gdpr-bar hidden>
    <div class="ganguram-delivery-progress__bar-fill" data-gdpr-bar-fill></div>
  </div>
  <p class="ganguram-delivery-progress__message" data-gdpr-message hidden></p>
  <p class="ganguram-delivery-progress__charge" data-gdpr-charge hidden></p>
  <ul class="ganguram-delivery-progress__services" data-gdpr-services hidden></ul>
</div>
